            <div class="hca-layout__container--body-content">
              <p class="hca-typography--body-1">If column sorting is enabled, sort the most important data by default and display a sorted state in the column header. If the user clicks on a column that is already sorted, reverse the sort order and rotate the sort icon.</p>
